video.title: The Prince of Tennis ~ Match! Tennis Juniors ~
video.synopsis: A tennis whiz beats the odds to excel on the court while juggling school and inspiring teammates. Based on the hit manga series by Takeshi Konomi.

episodes.synopsis: Mild-mannered student Qi Ying encounters quiet, gifted tennis player Lu Xia, who defeats Huang Jing in a match. Coach Qi Na phones Lu Xia's father.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: In a heated qualifying match against Zhang Baiyang, Lu Xia showcases his mastery in strategy and draws the attention of tennis journalist Xiaosha.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Yan Zhiming's analytical style proves to be a tough challenge for Lu Xia, who turns the table in his own favor. Qiao Chen meets Lu Xiangqian.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: In a match on the grass court, Xiaosha asks Lu Xiangqian why he left pro tennis. Qiao Chen and Lu Xia gear up for a high-stakes match.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: At the national men's school tournament, Qiao Chen and Lu Xia represent Yu Qing in a doubles match against a Yuhang school team.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Yu Feng captain Xu Ziping tells Xiaosha about his team's struggles with their former coach. Baiyang makes an unprecedented shot.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Lu Xia sustains an injury but proceeds with his match against Yu Feng's Yiwu. Yu Qing draws positive attention over Lu Xia's performance.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: As all the teams gear up for the citywide qualifying tournament, Lu Xia and teammate He Xinglong bond and agree to be training partners.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Mu Siyang challenges Lu Xia to a match in order to push him to be his best. Lu Xia's whereabouts are unknown during the day of the tournament.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Determined to defeat the Yu Qing team, Guo Zi coach Guan Yue lends a hand to Yu Qing's opponents and prepares to play against Zhuo Zhi.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: In a high-stakes tournament against Guo Zi, Tang Jiale risks losing steam while Qiao Chen and Zhang Baiyang bicker endlessly.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: In a thrilling match against Zhuo Yu, Lu Xia practices a new, unexpected technique. Guan Yue faces off against Zhuo Zhi.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Yu Qing members watch Yu Feng's Xu Ziping play in a match. Lu Xiangqian sets up Lu Xia to coach Qi Ying, who encounters the Ying Cai team.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: No. 3 High School's abrasive Ya Jiuxin riles up Qiao Chen. While Lu Xia plays Zhuo Zhi, Zhiming realizes that Lu Xia must change his strategy.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Zhiming and Qi Ying help the team prepare for their exams. On the day of the tournament, a mishap puts the Yu Feng team in a precarious position.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Qiao Chen meets his match in No. 3 High School player Shen Qianshi, who uses his own tactics against him. Lu Xia and Jiuxin face off.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: In his most challenging match yet, Lu Xia teaches Jiuxin a lesson. Dayong expresses his concerns about Siyang's X-ray results.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Hai Guang team's Yuan Chi arrives at a Yu Qing practice and challenges Siyang to a match. Chi Dayong and Jiale battle a Xing Yao doubles team.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: The Yu Qing team embarks on a new training program in their captain's absence. Xinglong considers quitting tennis.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Yu Qing loses in a friendly match to Yu Feng players. Xinglong feels torn between his team and his father's shop.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Ahead of its high-stakes challenge against Yu Feng, the Yu Qing team set out for the hills in search of a box left behind by their predecessors.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Lu Xia looks after Qi Ying when she falls ill. To redeem their previous losses, Yu Qing players gear up for their next round of matches against Yu Feng.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: At the lottery ceremony, Yu Qing encounters formidable opponent Xing Yao High School. Zhiming tells  Dayong that he must catch up with Jiale in speed.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: No. 6 High School coach Liu Ye challenges Lu Xia to a match and tells Lu Xiangqian that Lu Xia should explore his own playing style.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Zhiming encourages Yu Qing to draw inspiration from No. 6 High School's team dynamics. Kui Jian's unconventional style tests Baiyang's limits.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Xing Yao players' skills impress their Yu Qing opponents. With his injury showing no improvement, Siyang faces a dilemma.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: As Yu Qing players prepare for their highly anticipated match against Xing Yao, Lu Xiangqian helps Lu Xia realize that his biggest rival is himself.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: With Lu Xia out of the tournament, Yu Qing must reshuffle positions and formulate a new strategy. Zhiming encounters a childhood playmate.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Huang Jing challenges Lu Xia to a match. Coach Qi Na urges Siyang to forgo the tournament and focus on his recovery.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Baiyang and Zhiming find themselves chasing the scoreboard in a doubles match against Xing Yao. An unexpected incident befalls a Yu Qing player.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Xinglong takes his Xing Yao opponent by surprise. Zhuo Zhi dazzles spectators with a never-before-seen serve.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Dayong tells the team about Siyang's long-term injury. Siyang chooses to persevere in his match against Xing Yao captain Ji Jingwu.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Yu Qing's celebratory mood wears off with unfortunate news from Siyang's doctor. Zhuo Zhi offers Siyang his support.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: Lu Xia discovers a greater calling in tennis: teamwork. Siyang bids Yu Qing members a sentimental farewell before leaving for treatment abroad.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Days ahead of the provincial finals, Jingwu promises Siyang he will help prepare Yu Qing for their matches against Hai Guang.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Dayong and Jiale agree to pair up once again as a doubles team. Hai Guang captain Bai Shiting must withdraw from the tournament due to a surgery.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Jiale gives Zhuo Zhi encouragement. During the first doubles match of the tournament, the Hai Guang duo turns up the heat on Qiao Chen and Baiyang.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: An unexpected incident threatens to hold Yu Qing back. Zhiming takes the lead in a close singles match.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: Hai Guang player Yuan Chi vows to defeat Zhuo Zhi, who's pushed to the limit. Lu Xia and Tian Zilong face off in an unpredictable match.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Qi Ying helps boost Lu Xia's morale while he's on the verge of losing. Months later, Yu Qing members reflect on a challenging and rewarding season.
episodes.title: Episode 40
